Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:09.66,*Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,470)}{\a3}追尋光與影的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:16.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:19.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花鎮車站
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:21.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼還會在這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:23.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我們來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:25.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在溫泉街再住一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:27.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花街溫泉不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.65,0:23:28.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:30.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:31.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:33.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:34.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再住一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:38.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:24:00.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 看起來是條剛留下不久的新的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.68,0:24:06.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.95,0:24:08.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是事故 是謀殺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.85,0:24:10.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
